Invocation Name: agra guide
des:
Turn the pages of history with an ancient city. Revealing a wonderful tapestry of life, the city of Agra gracefully stands in Uttar Pradesh. Explore what Agra has to offer through this Alexa travel guide.

Some things you can say:
"Alexa, launch Agra Guide",
"Alexa, ask Agra Guide what are the top five things to do",
"Alexa, ask Agra Guide to tell me about Agra",
"Alexa, ask Agra Guide tell me the news",
"Alexa, ask Agra Guide where I should go"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
